<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-cmn">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>英雄节之“投”怀送宝</title>
    <meta name="description" content="宝开彩票">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=750,user-scalable=no">
    <script>
        var match,
            scale,
            TARGET_WIDTH = 750;
        if (match = navigator.userAgent.match(/Android (\d+\.\d+)/)) {
            if (parseFloat(match[1]) < 4.4) {
                TARGET_WIDTH++;
                scale = window.screen.width / TARGET_WIDTH;
                document.querySelector('meta[name="viewport"]').setAttribute('content', 'width=' + TARGET_WIDTH + ', initial-scale = ' + scale + ', target-densitydpi=device-dpi ,user-scalable=no');
            }
        } else {
            document.querySelector('meta[name="viewport"]').setAttribute('content', 'width=' + TARGET_WIDTH);
        }
    </script>   
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{$path_img}/images/activity/2017_June/activity01/mb/images/main.css">
    <script src="{$path_js}/js/activity/2017_June/activity01/mb/jquery-3.2.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="{$path_js}/js/activity/2017_June/activity01/mb/index.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div id="main">
    <div id="main-body">
        <a href="phlotto://go_lottolobby" id="logo-link"></a>
        <div id="sign-up"></div>
        <div id="activity-content">
            <div id="content-info">
                用户在活动期间（共六天）内，每日累计充值≥200元，并在当日达到相应流水要求后，次日即可领取对应活动奖金。
            </div>
            <div id="normal-player">
                <img src="{$path_img}/images/activity/2017_June/activity01/mb/images/normal_03.png" alt="">  &nbsp;普通玩家奖励
            </div>
            <div id="normal-list">
                <table>
                    <tr class="normal-tr1">
                        <td class="td1">当日累计存款金额</td>
                        <td class="td2">奖金比例</td>
                        <td class="td3">销量/充值倍数</td>
                        <td>奖金上限</td>

                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="tr2" rowspan="3">≥200</td>
                        <td>5%</td>
                        <td>6</td>
                        <td class="tr2" rowspan="3">16666</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>11%</td>
                        <td>12</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>24%</td>
                        <td>24</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

            </div>
            <div id="vip-player">
                <img src="{$path_img}/images/activity/2017_June/activity01/mb/images/vip_03.png" alt=""> &nbsp;VIP玩家奖励
            </div>
            <div id="vip-list">
                <table>
                    <tr class="vip-tr1">
                        <td class="td1">当日累计存款金额</td>
                        <td class="td2">奖金比例</td>
                        <td class="td3">销量/充值倍数</td>
                        <td>奖金上限</td>

                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="tr2" rowspan="3">≥5000</td>
                        <td>6%</td>
                        <td>6</td>
                        <td class="tr2" rowspan="3">36666</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>13%</td>
                        <td>12</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>28%</td>
                        <td>24</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

            </div>
            <div id="content-tip">
                <div id="qualification">
                    <div id="qual1"><span>活动资格：</span>流水要求=当日总销量/当日累计充值金额</div>
                    <div id="qual2">赠送奖金=当日累计充值金额*赠送比例</div>
                </div>
                <div id="example">
                    <div id="exam1"><span>例：</span>1、普通用户A当日累计充值1,000元，当日销量为12,000，打够了12倍流水，奖金</div>
                    <div class="exam3">为1,000*11%=110元。</div>
                    <div class="exam2">2、VIP用户当日累计充值5,000元，当日销量为120,000，打够24倍流水，奖金为</div>
                    <div class="exam3">5,000*28%=1,400元。</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="activity-rule">
            <div id="rule-list">
                <ul>
                    <li>1.活动返奖，参与游戏只限于宝开彩票旗舰版及宝开彩票专业版。</li>
                    <li>2.投注必须为已开奖注单，视为有效投注，奖励计算依据用户在活动期间内的有效投注量</li>
                    <li class="escape">审核计算， PT、宝开游艺FHX、六合彩、骰宝大小单双销量不计算在活动销量内。</li>
                    <li>3.本次活动采取报名制，用户需要点击“我要报名”后才能获取活动奖金。</li>
                    <li class="escape">注：VIP3（包含VIP3）以上用户无需报名即可参加。</li>
                    <li>4.平台新注册用户，首存优惠不得与本次活动同时享受。当首存优惠领取后，方可参与本</li>
                    <li class="escape">次活动。</li>
                    <li>5.本次活动包含上下级充值，如未满足下一等级销量倍数则按照上一等级奖金比例派发</li>
                    <li class="escape">（例：12>销量/充值倍数>6按照6倍奖金比例派发）。</li>
                    <li>6.超级2000玩法按实际投注额的80%进行结算。如：用户超级2000玩法中投注额为</li>
                    <li class="escape">1,000，则结算销量为1,000*80%=800。</li>
                    <li>7.活动奖金于活动开始后每日次日18:00点前派发活动前一日奖金。</li>
                    <li>8.活动期间禁止任何作弊行为，一经发现平台将取消参与活动资格，严重者将被冻结账号</li>
                    <li class="escape">处理。</li>
                    <li>9.宝开平台保留活动最终解释权。</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="footer">
            <div id="rights">©2003-2017 宝开彩票 All Rights Reserved</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
    
<input id="signStatus" type="hidden" value="{$signStatus}"/>
<input id="status" type="hidden" value="{$status}"/>
<input id="token" type="hidden" value="{$token}"/>
<input id="awardStatus" type="hidden" value="{$awardStatus}"/>
    
</body>
</html>
